).

General distribution: This is a widespread species in North America . In Canada it ranges from Nova Scotia to Manitoba; in the United States from New York to Florida, across Texas and the Great Plains to Montana, Colorado, New Mexico , Arizona, and California; and R. ou is also found in Bermuda and the Dominican Republic; and Mexico south through Central America , Venezuela , and the Andes to Ecuador (
